{"id": 1592, "genre": 1000, "title": "在目前这种环境下，你觉得什么可以被叫做“真正的聪明”？", "description": "很多关于聪明的看法实际上是一些“小聪明”，比如察言观色会说话什么的…你觉得当代咋样才算一个能独立思考的聪明人呢？（题图来自：Andrice Arp）", "record_count": 44662, "comment_count": 100, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170328231531t0SZioYXMb3mICrn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-29T17:00:37Z", "questions": [{"id": 2082, "title": "在目前这种环境下，你觉得什么可以被叫做“真正的聪明”？", "content": "在目前这种环境下，你觉得什么可以被叫做“聪明”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 184938, "content": "控制信息摄取量，明白没那么多事“不能错过”", "image": "img/option/option/2017032910545578ywlrTWBK49YxnZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 184939, "content": "明辨信息来源，分得清情绪和事实", "image": "img/option/option/20170329105504o7VaF5Pm2IdecBt4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 184940, "content": "有思考习惯，而不是用知乎的“如何评价”替自己评价", "image": "img/option/option/20170329105513WSCmEyedHiXcw9Kh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 184941, "content": "会用简单语言解释复杂问题，不故弄玄虚耍花腔", "image": "img/option/option/20170329105522Vs4gO27otFWhiaIz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 184942, "content": "不被“刻板印象”和“固化思维”牵着走", "image": "img/option/option/20170329105531ac4Ql6tSsME8GvRk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 184944, "content": "不仅仅是“mark”，学会知识的内化", "image": "img/option/option/20170329105541VUAQxDBdNZoXR9cu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 184945, "content": "生活不为了别人的观赏和点赞", "image": "img/option/option/20170329105554EwITW35tYzjAbcxR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 184946, "content": "知道一流的作品值得花时间，不需要别人“10分钟帮你读完xx”", "image": "img/option/option/20170329105607aYREq3z06tKHV8jX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}